title: Defender Pro Utilities ( Including 100% Permanent File Delete )
description:
Defender Pro Utilities is an application that contains several nifty features. However, what will catch the attention of most pirates is the File Wiper module, allowing for the 100% permanent deletion of files using the Military Standard Wipe option. This option is permanent, there is no known way of ever retrieving this data. Use this before the party van pulls into your driveway and get rid off all that chocolate pudding on your drive.

Hope this helps someone out.
